description: Ayane starts work at Kazuto's house as a maid, but we all know what that means, Kazuto's at it again, boffing those beauties day and night. Seems he has a little more then a sex thing with Momiji. He wants her over Ayane. Well, that fire's up the competition. Which girl can make the other girl twiddle in the middle first? Katzuto promises to make whoppee with the one who who wins. Who will it be?
title: Momiji
